    • getReferences

      public static Map<String,​TypeReference> getReferences​(Collection<MessageFields> structs)
      Transforms the given struct definitions into references so telemetry and telecommand messages can reference them. Primitive type references from Corfu are added by default.
      Parameters:
      structs - the structs from an app configuration
      Returns:
      a reference map that can map types from the Corfu config to Java objects / type references
